data.description:
Discover your ideal home in a prime location! This 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem is perfectly situated on a corner cul-de-sac lot with a spacious backyard. The master bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor, while two additional bedrooms offer versatility upstairs. 
Enjoy quick access to shopping, groceries, restaurants, and numerous nearby schools. Plus, commute effortlessly with access to Loop 375 and I-10. Don't miss this opportunity to call this convenient and comfortable property your own. Schedule a showing today!
